Originality/value: Studies of managerial teams in the field of interpersonal relations are rare. This paper contributes to fill this gap by selecting TMT teams as subjects for research. The study reported in this paper contributes to current understanding of the nature of relationship between trust and positive relationships in team.&#x0D;
Keywords: trust, positive relationships, top management team (TMT), trust within team&#x0D;
Paper type: Research paper.
